<! [CDATA[
 Recreational Equipment, Inc. Logo
Recreational Equipment, Inc., commonly known as REI, is an American retail and outdoor recreation services corporation. It is organized as a consumers' co-operative. REI sells sporting goods, camping gear, travel equipment, and clothing. It also offers services such as outdoor-oriented vacations and courses. REI operates 165 retail stores in 39 states. It also receives orders via mail-order catalogs and the internet. REI’s annual revenue for 2019 was US$3.12 billion.
You can download theREIlogo on full-version of the page.
